                1055
            ],
            "ignore": false,
            "order": 5,
            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": " $$ c_n(m) = \\mu\\left(\\frac{n}{(n,m)}\\right) \\frac{\\varphi(n)}{\\varphi\\left(\\frac{n}{(n,m)}\\right)} $$",
            "line_with_spans": [
