            ],
            "ignore": false,
            "order": 6,
            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": " *Proof.* First of all, suppose that  $m = 1$ . Recall an elementary formula that",
            "line_with_spans": [
                {
                    "category_type": "text_span",
                    "poly": [
                        355,
                        1075,
