            "text": " $$ c_n(1) = \\sum_{t=1}^n \\zeta_n^t \\sum_{k|(t,n)} \\mu(k) = \\sum_{k|n} \\mu(k) \\sum_{\\substack{1 \\le t \\le n, \\\\ k|(t,n)}} \\zeta_n^t = \\sum_{k|n} \\mu(k) \\sum_{\\substack{1 \\le t' \\le \\frac{n}{k}}} (\\zeta_n^k)^{t'} $$",
            "line_with_spans": [
                {
