            "text": " where  $t' = \\frac{t}{k}$ . Since  $\\zeta_n^k$  is a primitive  $\\frac{n}{k}$ -th root of 1, the last sum gives 1 if  $k = n$  and 0 if  $k < n$ . Hence,  $c_n(1) = \\mu(n)$ .",
            "line_with_spans": [
