            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": " Now, the result follows from  $|N| = \\frac{\\varphi(n)}{\\varphi(d)}$  and  $c_d(1) = \\mu(d)$  by the first paragraph.  $\\Box$ ",
            "line_with_spans": [
